## Problem Solved

${data.problem_solved}

## Tools Used

${data.tools_used}

## Workflow Steps

${data.workflow_steps}

## Key Learning

${data.key_learning}

## Files Included

- README.md
- setup-guide.md
- linkedin-post.md
- workflow-summary.md

## Project Status

Completed basic documentation generation workflow.

## Date Created

${today}
`,

  setup_content: `# Setup Guide - ${data.project_name}

